strings.Value: "Well, is anyone going hunting. We on hare diet again?"
"Well, who's for dinner, ha, ha, hmm... I want meat..."
"Ha. Joker. Why don't you go fry some wild boar for us."
"Don't you think there's already enough death and pain in the world? Even without killing someone just to fill your stomach?"
"Ha ha ha, SO funny. It doesn't mean you're wrong though. {name}, these meals stick in my throat."
"Chin up, Reg. These meals aren't so bad. Better than the slop we ate as children..."
